449
00:27:02,843 --> 00:27:04,321
Selamat malam.

450
00:27:08,015 --> 00:27:11,327
AI menyuap anak-anak kita?

451
00:27:11,351 --> 00:27:13,705
Aku rasa itu mengalahkan
stiker grafik.

452
00:27:18,387 --> 00:27:20,104
Sial.

453
00:27:20,128 --> 00:27:22,337
<i>- Dilarang memaki.</i>
- Maaf.

454
00:27:22,362 --> 00:27:25,318
<i>Aku hanya bercanda. Persetan.</i>

455
00:27:25,342 --> 00:27:27,946
- Bagaimana kau masuk ke sana?
<i>- Jangan khawatir soal itu.</i>

456
00:27:27,970 --> 00:27:29,595
Kau bisa beri aku waktu
memakai gawai lebih?

457
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:30,907
<i>Itu...</i>

458
00:27:30,931 --> 00:27:33,056
<i>Oke. Penyuara jemala, sobat.</i>

459
00:27:33,248 --> 00:27:35,267
<i>Ini harus jadi rahasia kecil kita.</i>

460
00:27:35,292 --> 00:27:37,497
<i>Jangan beritahu siapa-siapa.
Setuju?</i>

461
00:27:37,521 --> 00:27:38,814
Setuju.

462
00:27:49,182 --> 00:27:50,407
Cal?

