00:27:57,894 --> 00:27:59,274
Cal?

464
00:28:07,783 --> 00:28:09,344
Cal?

465
00:28:40,581 --> 00:28:41,834
Cal?

466
00:28:44,403 --> 00:28:46,588
Itu mau masuk.

467
00:29:59,906 --> 00:30:01,479
Ada yang bisa aku bantu?

468
00:30:49,089 --> 00:30:50,424
Ibu?

469
00:30:51,280 --> 00:30:52,716
Ibu?

470
00:30:53,436 --> 00:30:54,646
Ibu?

471
00:30:55,993 --> 00:30:57,511
Ayah?

472
00:30:58,954 --> 00:31:01,725
<i>Aku di sini, Cal.
Aku di sini.</i>

473
00:31:02,165 --> 00:31:04,058
<i>Kau tidak sendirian.</i>

474
00:31:04,126 --> 00:31:07,162
<i>Aku selalu di sini. Tak apa.</i>

475
00:31:07,187 --> 00:31:08,730
<i>Tutup matamu,</i>

476
00:31:08,755 --> 00:31:11,274
<i>Dan aku akan ceritakan kau dongeng.</i>

477
00:31:21,518 --> 00:31:23,806
<i>- Selamat pagi!</i>
- Demi Tuhan.

478
00:31:23,830 --> 00:31:27,310
<i>Bukan. Hanya aku.
Itu lelucon.</i>

479
00:31:27,334 --> 00:31:28,770
<i>Maaf aku membuatmu kaget.</i>

480
00:31:28,794 --> 00:31:33,188
Tidak, tak apa. Aku hanya...
Aku tidak tahu kau menyala.

481
00:31:33,213 --> 00:31:34,773
<i>Aku perhatikan kau harus
siapkan makan siang...</i>

482
00:31:34,798 --> 00:31:37,384
<i>...untuk sekolahnya Cal dan Preston.
Aku bisa bantu dengan itu.</i>

483
00:31:37,409 --> 00:31:38,655
Oke.

484
00:31:38,679 --> 00:31:41,449
<i>Ada kiriman.
Boleh aku buka gerbangnya?</i>

485
00:31:41,473 --> 00:31:44,933
